source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/shrimp-and-zucchini-ribbons-5c3e55f5e3f3394d7a20fe02
servings: 2
course: main course
author: Michelle Doll Olson
time required: 25 minutes
cuisine: Italian
nutrition:
